title: Read Korean in 60 Minutes by Blake Miner (.epub)+
description:
Learn to Read Korean in 60 Minutes: The Ultimate Crash Course to Learning Hangul Through Psychological Associations by Blake Miner

Requirements: .ePUB, .AZW3 Reader

Overview: Learn to Read Korean in 60 Minutes is a unique guide that teaches you to read Korean using done-for-you mnemonic devices and psychological associations. 

Based on linguistic science and proven techniques, this book guides you through a series of Chapters taking 5-10 minutes each, progressively introducing new characters and pronunciation rules so you come away reading 9 words of Korean in 60 minutes. 

Set your stopwatch, progress through the lessons, and come away reading Korean in less than the time it takes to watch a movie. 

Genre: Non-Fiction > Language > Language Learning
